            <div class="title">
                Representation Of The People Bill
            </div>

            <div class="right-arrow">
                    <a href="/Commons/1948-02-16/debates/161e061c-ddc9-4beb-a806-4e8384cc859c/PublicServiceVehicles(Brighton)" class="next" title="Go to the next debate">
