<p class="">How does the right hon. Gentleman know that?</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-8e823148-fbb0-48c0-90b1-ccd77bfb7675" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
