                Mr. Titterington
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-f124c362-5b6e-4ec2-b216-f51034fc72ad" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
