<div class="content-item" id="contribution-83780fdd-aaa6-4313-b6e2-6403c15b644a">
    <div class="col-md-9 edit-fail-error">
        <div class="alert alert-danger" id="alert-83780fdd-aaa6-4313-b6e2-6403c15b644a">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign"></span>The edit just sent has not been saved.  The following error was returned:
        </div>
