        <div class="col-md-9 nohighlight member-container">
            <h2 class="memberLink col-md-9" id="member-link-46b8de09-028c-49bf-ab44-196bf212d3b8">
                Mr. Woodburn
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-46b8de09-028c-49bf-ab44-196bf212d3b8" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
               data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
               data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1948-02-16/debates/2412df98-4b93-4a3a-be82-7a3b0a828318/RepresentationOfThePeopleBill#contribution-46b8de09-028c-49bf-ab44-196bf212d3b8">
                <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div><span class="share-text">Share</span>
            </a>
        </div>

    


    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">If university representation gives the advantages of proportional representation, is it not the case that, under this proportional representation in the universities, not one Labour Member has been sent to this House?</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-46b8de09-028c-49bf-ab44-196bf212d3b8" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
                           data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
                           data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1948-02-16/debates/2412df98-4b93-4a3a-be82-7a3b0a828318/RepresentationOfThePeopleBill#contribution-46b8de09-028c-49bf-ab44-196bf212d3b8">
                            <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div>&nbsp;Share
                        </a>
                    </div>

        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="clearfix"></div>
</div>





<div class="content-item" id="contribution-989f2a2a-6f7d-4cc4-8baf-a85423f0c4e9">
    <div class="col-md-9 edit-fail-error">
        <div class="alert alert-danger" id="alert-989f2a2a-6f7d-4cc4-8baf-a85423f0c4e9">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign"></span>The edit just sent has not been saved.  The following error was returned:
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-9 multiple-edit-warning">
        <div class="alert alert-warning" id="warning-989f2a2a-6f7d-4cc4-8baf-a85423f0c4e9">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign"></span>This content has already been edited and is awaiting review.
        </div>
    </div>

        <div class="col-md-9 nohighlight member-container">
            <h2 class="memberLink col-md-9" id="member-link-989f2a2a-6f7d-4cc4-8baf-a85423f0c4e9">
                Sir J. Anderson
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-989f2a2a-6f7d-4cc4-8baf-a85423f0c4e9" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
               data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
               data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1948-02-16/debates/2412df98-4b93-4a3a-be82-7a3b0a828318/RepresentationOfThePeopleBill#contribution-989f2a2a-6f7d-4cc4-8baf-a85423f0c4e9">
                <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div><span class="share-text">Share</span>
            </a>
        </div>

    


    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">I will come to that point, because it is a very serious one. I am saying that we get the advantages that are claimed for proportional representation in the case of the university franchise and we do have also—this point has not previously been made—</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-989f2a2a-6f7d-4cc4-8baf-a85423f0c4e9" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
                           data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
                           data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1948-02-16/debates/2412df98-4b93-4a3a-be82-7a3b0a828318/RepresentationOfThePeopleBill#contribution-989f2a2a-6f7d-4cc4-8baf-a85423f0c4e9">
                            <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div>&nbsp;Share
                        </a>
                    </div>

        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="clearfix"></div>
</div>





<div class="content-item" id="contribution-42a4dbde-f750-48bc-9dcc-762e2289b899">
    <div class="col-md-9 edit-fail-error">
