        </div>

    


    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">Would not the right hon Gentleman agree that without three Members in university constituencies, he does not get any of the advantages of proportional representation?</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-42a4dbde-f750-48bc-9dcc-762e2289b899" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
                           data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
                           data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1948-02-16/debates/2412df98-4b93-4a3a-be82-7a3b0a828318/RepresentationOfThePeopleBill#contribution-42a4dbde-f750-48bc-9dcc-762e2289b899">
                            <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div>&nbsp;Share
                        </a>
                    </div>

        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="clearfix"></div>
