            <h2 class="memberLink col-md-9" id="member-link-29c00054-8cff-4a06-9139-f34d4d6044c0">
                Mr. Wilfrid Roberts  (Cumberland, Northern)
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-29c00054-8cff-4a06-9139-f34d4d6044c0" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
