<p class="">The hon. Gentleman has forgotten that the Liberals voted against proportional representation when the 1918 Measure was before the House.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-d5dd5262-d5d1-495d-9d77-98a63d5536bf" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
