<p class="">No, I do not. I want to know whether or not our right to ask for an elucidation of a Ruling by the Chair is in question. I never sought at any time in my argument to do more than that. I want to know whether your last remark constitutes a denial of the right of a Member of the House of Commons to ask for an elucidation from the occupant of the Chair on his previous Ruling.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
